## ததஅக

[ ellaiyōṭi ]  
  
பெ. id. `boundary runner  
a village officer usu. a pancama  
whose testimony in case of boundary disputesis accepted by the disputants  
when he showsthe boundary line by running round it afterhaving been solemnly sworn to discharge hisduty as almost a divine arbitrator by being required to go through certain aweinspiringceremonies before the shrine of the villagedeity; கிராமதேவதையின் கோயிலின்முன்னே சிலசடங்குகளைச்செய்து பிறகு எல்லையைக்காட்டி வழக்கைத்தீர்ப்போன். loc